room_title: Escape room "Transfiguration" by Unlock Escape Rooms in Fresno
room_description: The School of Witchcraft & Wizardry is a series of 4 escape rooms. Visit classrooms inspired by J.K. Rowling's Harry Potter and Hogwarts School for Wizards.  Harry Potter fans will recognize clues and props inspired by this epic series, but no prior knowledge of the books/movies is required to enjoy this room. Play one room or experience all 4 rooms: TRANSFIGURATION, HERBOLOGY, POTIONS and SPELLS & POTIONS.  Rooms change periodically.  So don't delay!
